nodes.text: The Arbitrator was a Venator-class Star Destroyer in the Republic Navy during the Clone Wars.

Around 21 BBY, the Arbitrator was destroyed during an assault launched by General Grievous's Recusant-class light destroyer, but Clone Commander Cody and a Jedi Knight were able to save the surviving crew from being captured by Grievous with the aid of Jedi Master Obi-Wan Kenobi and Jedi Padawan Ahsoka Tano.
